entries.title_d: Command wants to know more about these mercenaries. They have discovered a patrol of their ships moving across the system. You are to capture one of the Neutron fighters in that group and escort it back to Imperial hands.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Capture a Coynite Neutron
entries.thanks_5: They will be remembered as heroes.
entries.thanks_4: You may have destroyed them but I will never bow.
entries.thanks_3: They will be remembered as heroes.
entries.thanks_2: You have not yet defeated the Coynite.
entries.thanks_1: You are a mighty pilot, but they will be back.
entries.taunt_5: Mercy is for the weak. I shall crush you!
entries.taunt_4: So you want to play rough, eh? How about some of this! And a little of that! And a whole boat load of this!
entries.taunt_3: The time for mercy is at an end.
entries.target_disabled: Targets engines are off line. Close the distance and prepare to capture.
entries.recovery_success: We have the Coynite Mercenary. Nice work pilot. Head for home.
entries.quest_recover_d: Once disabled, move in close to the Neutron and wait for the capture process to begin.
entries.quest_location_d: The target vessel and its escort are moving through the Dathomir system. Capture that ship before it can leave the system.
entries.quest_escort_d: Follow and protect the Neutron to a safe jump location. Command is very interested in finding out more about the Coynite and why they are in this system.
entries.panic_5: My brothers will kill me before allowing Imperial scum to take me captive.
entries.panic_4: My brothers will kill me before allowing Imperial scum to take me captive.
entries.panic_3: I would rather die then be a servant of the Empire.
entries.panic_2: My nobel death shall be sung in the high places of the universe.
entries.panic_1: My brothers will kill me before allowing Imperial scum to take me captive.
entries.failed_escape: Your orders were to capture us that ship. Make your excuses to your superior.
entries.failed_destroy: Your orders were to capture us that ship. Make your excuses to your superior.
entries.complete: Nice work. Return to your superior officer for debriefing.
entries.capture_phase_2: Fine, fine... We will come with you. Just lay off the pressure, will you?
entries.capture_phase_1: What are you doing? I haven't done anything wrong.
entries.arrival_phase_2: We have transfered the location of the fighter to your nav computer. Capture the fighters leader and escort it back to Imperial space.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Getting lock on Coynite Mercenary fighter. Stand by for coordinates.
entries.angry_disable: By Coyn! My engines are offline. Your aim is true pilot.
entries.abort: Yeah, thats right get out of here. I always knew that Imperial pilots were cowards.
